-- Tullow Completes $1.35 Billion Purchase of Heritage's Oil Assets in Uganda
-- Dara Doyle
-- 2010-07-27T06:07:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/tullow-completes-1-35-billion-purchase-of-heritage-s-oil-assets-in-uganda.html

          
          
             Tullow Oil Plc said it completed the
acquisition of Heritage Oil and Gas Limited’s Ugandan assets for
$1.35 billion, with an “additional contractual settlement”
amount of $100 million.  
          
          


  


        